{"tid":2109263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警察同納粹德軍真係無分別","createTime":"2020-07-15T06:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T05:13:07.000Z","uid":35063,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"49a0eb21ff9d8f877426e87cdfb4f1c1b99f332f","tid":2109263,"uid":35063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:17:34.000Z","msg":"講緊係帶比人個種恐懼感，因為皇軍咁無人管到，根本大撚哂<br />\n啱啱去個客屋企做野，準備走個時<br />\n有兩個自稱警察既人問邊度係幾多號，咁啱就係我地呢個單位。<br />\n個客（應該係媽媽）一聽到係警察，嚇到即刻拉閘，問咩事<br />\n原來係重案組上黎叫當事人聯絡番佢地拎番啲證物走，唔係就會充公咁話<br />\n斷估應該係被補手足既家庭<br />\n雖然客觀講佢地語氣都算係平和，但根本而家一聽到警察兩個字就恐慌既人大有人在<br />\n因為呢班人帶比大家既傷害實在太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc798da45c2ded8289829a44b919a4c34a631fda","tid":2109263,"uid":252142,"like":2,"dislike":92,"score":-90,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:19:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e0e5f30c593cdffb5a119a5985a998ee2249969","tid":2109263,"uid":16534,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"dc798da45c2ded8289829a44b919a4c34a631fda","tid":2109263,"uid":252142,"like":2,"dislike":92,"score":-90,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:19:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:21:15.000Z","msg":"你呢隻5毛真係好撚煩"},{"pid":"df639e56b6d8cc9b43da06ce8b1bd3bdc332a798","tid":2109263,"uid":67346,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"dc798da45c2ded8289829a44b919a4c34a631fda","tid":2109263,"uid":252142,"like":2,"dislike":92,"score":-90,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:19:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:22:08.000Z","msg":"又見到你條傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8aa3671598784efb37b5d278aee3fc7a4354c31","tid":2109263,"uid":58209,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1HRtaay.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1HRtaay.jpg&h=dc70c62c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7235401f227baf5f